            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">2</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，《小学语文教学》以双月刊形式独立出版，特邀叶圣陶、袁微子、李伯棠、陆静山、霍懋征、袁瑢、高惠莹为顾问。</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt"> <br>
            </span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">4</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，山西教育杂志社与太原市群众艺术馆联合举办了</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">园丁书画展览</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">”</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">大型活动。</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt"> <br>
            </span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">6</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，省文教委员会、省工会、山西广播电台、山西教育杂志社联合举办了全省教工</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">五讲四美</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">”</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">有奖征歌活动。</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">9</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，山西教育杂志社举行《山西教育》杂志创刊</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">26</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">周年、复刊</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">100</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">期纪念活动，省委第一书记霍士廉题词：</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">开发智力资源，启迪建设人才。</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">”</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">12</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，叶圣陶为《小学语文教学》杂志题写刊名。</span></div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 49.9pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" width="67">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1983</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">年</span></div>
            </td>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 371.4pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" valign="top" width="495">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，《小学语文教学》成为全国小学语文教学研究会会刊，由山西省教育厅和全国小学语文教学研究会共同主办。主编为袁微子。</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt"> <br>
            </span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">辛亮任党总支书记、社长、总编辑，张秉谦任副社长、副总编辑。</span></div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 49.9pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" width="67">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1985</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">年</span></div>
            </td>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 371.4pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" valign="top" width="495">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，《小学语文教学》改为月刊。《成人教育》也改为月刊，成为全国成人教育期刊中的第一份月刊。</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt"> <br>
            </span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">5</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">15</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">日，《山西教育报》试刊，全国人大常委会委员长彭真为本报题写了报头。</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt"> <br>
            </span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">8</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">5</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">日，《山西教育报》正式创刊，为四开四版周报，周一出版。省委副书记、省长王森浩为《山西教育报》创刊题词：</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">办好《山西教育报》，推动教育体制改革。</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">”</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">省委常委、省委宣传部部长张维庆在《山西教育报》创刊报上发表了题为《振兴山西，首先要振兴教育》的文章。</span></div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 49.9pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" width="67">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1986</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">年</span></div>
            </td>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 371.4pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" valign="top" width="495">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，《山西教育报》面向全国公开发行。</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">&nbsp;<br>
            </span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">6</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，东北、华北</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">8</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">省（市）教育综合月刊第一次协作会在太原举行，由山西教育杂志社主办。</span></div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 49.9pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" width="67">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1987</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">年</span></div>
            </td>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 371.4pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" valign="top" width="495">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">5</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，山西教育杂志社更名为</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">山西教育报刊社</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">”</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">。</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">&nbsp;<br>
            </span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">7</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，张道义任党总支书记，张秉谦任总编辑、社长，夏立纯任副社长、副总编辑，文琴任副总编辑，何创明任副社长。</span></div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 49.9pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" width="67">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1988</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">年</span></div>
            </td>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 371.4pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" valign="top" width="495">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，经省新闻出版局批准，《山西教育报》改为对开四版周报；《成人教育》更名为《山西成人教育》。</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">2</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">日，国家教委副主任柳斌为《小学语文教学》题词：</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">培养良好的语文能力，发展儿童思维，开发儿童智力。</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">”&nbsp;<br>
            </span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">5</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，《山西教育》被评为</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">山西省首届优秀期刊</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">”</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">。《山西教育》编辑部举办了</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">全国中小学教师、学生、教育工作者硬笔书法大赛</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">”</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">和</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">全国中小学生</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">‘</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">心灵深处的秘密</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">’</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">同题作文大赛</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">”</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">。</span></div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 49.9pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" width="67">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1989</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">年</span></div>
            </td>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 371.4pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" valign="top" width="495">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，《山西教育》实行自办发行。</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt"> <br>
            </span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">9</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，张秉谦任总编辑、社长，夏立纯任党总支副书记、副社长，刘文华任副总编辑，赵义堂任副总编辑，何创明任副社长。实行总编辑负责制。</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt"> <br>
            </span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">11</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，《小学语文教学》编辑部倡议发起的</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">全国小学语文中青年教师阅读教学观摩活动</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">”</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">在成都市举行。来自全国</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">27</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">个省、市、自治区的</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">28</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">位教师上了观摩课，参加人员达</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">2300</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">余人。</span></div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 49.9pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" width="67">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1990</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">年</span></div>
            </td>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 371.4pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" valign="top" width="495">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，《山西教育报》由对开四版改为四开四版周报。</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt"> <br>
            </span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">4</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，《山西教育》编辑部组成</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">山西教育考察团</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">”</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">，骑自行车沿黄河对吕梁山中的</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">13</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">个山老贫县进行了实地考察，历时</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">30</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">天，行程</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">2500</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">公里。</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">&nbsp;<br>
            </span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">7</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，《山西成人教育》编辑部组成</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">太行山考察团</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">”</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">，骑自行车考察太行山区教育现状，行程</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1200</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">公里，途经</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">13</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">个县（区），历时</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">22</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">天。</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">&nbsp;<br>
            </span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">8</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">5</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">日，</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">山西教育报五周年庆祝大会及全国省级教育报新闻研讨会</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">”</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">在太原举行。来自全国</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">10</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">个省（市）教育报的负责同志参加了会议。</span></div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 49.9pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" width="67">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1991</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">年</span></div>
            </td>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 371.4pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" valign="top" width="495">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">7</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，《山西教育》杂志复刊</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">200</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">期，举办了</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">山西省中小学教学管理研讨会暨讲习班</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">”</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">。《山西成人教育》举办了创刊</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">10</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">周年庆祝大会及首期</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">全国成人教育理论研讨会</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">”</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">。</span></div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 49.9pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" width="67">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1992</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">年</span></div>
            </td>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 371.4pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" valign="top" width="495">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 9pt">3</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 9pt">月，《小学生之友》创刊。山西省副省长吴达才，著名作家冰心，全国劳动模范、特级教师斯霞，著名作家刘绍棠、蒋子龙、陈伯吹、刘白羽、马烽、孙谦、刘白羽，著名诗人冈夫，著名漫画家华君武，团中央书记处书记、全国少工委主任李克强和中国少年报社社长兼总编辑、中国少年儿童报刊工作者协会沈腴正，山西省教委副主任张原理等为该刊题词。</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 9pt"> <br>
            </span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 9pt">9</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 9pt">月，《小学语文教学》承办的</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 9pt">全国小学语文中青年教师不同风格、不同流派阅读教学观摩研讨会</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 9pt">”</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 9pt">在太原举行。听课教师来自全国</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 9pt">28</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 9pt">个省、市、自治区共</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 9pt">2600</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 9pt">余人。</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 9pt">11</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 9pt">月，《小学语文教学》编辑部在福建厦门举办</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 9pt">鼓浪屿之秋小学语文教改经验研讨会</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 9pt">”</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 9pt">。</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 9pt">《小学语文教学》加入中国语文报刊协会。被北京高校图书馆期刊工作研究会列为全国中文核心期刊。</span></div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 49.9pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" width="67">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1993</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">年</span></div>
            </td>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 371.4pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" valign="top" width="495">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，《山西教育》《山西成人教育》《小学语文教学》均由铅排胶印改为激光照排胶印。</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt"> <br>
            </span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">《小学生之友》编辑部与省教委普教处联合举办了第一届</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">全省小学生书画比赛</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">”</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">，之后连续九年举办了</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">山西省小学师生书画比赛</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">”</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">。</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt"> <br>
            </span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">7</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，杜康宁任副总编辑、副社长，王冬生任副总编辑。《山西教育》组建了全省各地（市）、县（区）通联工作站。《小学生之友》编辑部举办了首届</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">小学生暑假夏令营</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">”</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">。</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt"> <br>
            </span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">10</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，《山西成人教育》在中国成人教育学会期刊委员会举行的首届全国成人教育期刊校对评比中荣获第一名。</span></div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 49.9pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" width="67">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1994</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">年</span></div>
            </td>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 371.4pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" valign="top" width="495">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">5</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，《山西教育报》与省教委、省人民教育基金会、《山西日报》等共同举办《教师法》有奖知识竞赛。</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt"> <br>
            </span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">10</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，由省教委、山西日报社、省希望工程领导组牵头，《山西教育报》等</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">6</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">家新闻单位举行了</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">希望工程考察活动</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">”</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">。胡富国、郭裕怀、崔光祖等省领导亲临出发仪式并作了重要讲话。省委书记胡富国同志为此次活动题词。</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">《小学语文教学》被评为全国中文核心期刊。</span></div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 49.9pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" width="67">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1995</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">年</span></div>
            </td>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 371.4pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" valign="top" width="495">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，山西省教委等几家单位联合组织</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">三晋扫盲行</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">”</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">记者采访团，《山西教育》《山西教育报》《山西成人教育》三个编辑部参加。</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt"> <br>
            </span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">3</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，省教委主办、《小学生之友》承办的</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">全省小学生爱国主义教育知识竞赛</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">”</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">收到征稿</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">10</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">万余份，评出优胜奖</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">8000</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">名，组织奖</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">21</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">个，团体奖</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">29</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">个。</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt"> <br>
            </span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">3</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">14</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">日，李衍黔任党总支书记、副总编辑，刘文华为副处级调研员。</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">6</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，《山西教育报》与省教委联合组织了</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">星辰杯《中华人民共和国教育法》知识竞赛</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">”</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">，全省有</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">20</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">余万人参加了这次竞赛活动。</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">8</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">5</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">日，《山西教育报》举行创刊十周年庆祝大会。省委书记胡富国、省长孙文盛分别题词。</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">8</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">7</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">日，《山西教育报》由四开四版改为对开四版周报。</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt"> <br>
            </span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">9</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，省教委主办、报刊社承办了</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">山西省山老区教师度假周</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">”</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">活动。省领导胡富国、卢功勋、孙祥炎出席了开幕式。《山西成人教育》编辑部举办全省扫盲知识大赛，有</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">3</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">万余名读者参加。</span></div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 49.9pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" width="67">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1996</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">年</span></div>
            </td>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 371.4pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" valign="top" width="495">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，《山西成人教育》改为大</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">16K</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">本。《山西教育报》等三家新闻单位联合举办纪念《义务教育法》颁布</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">10</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">周年有奖征文活动。</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt"> <br>
            </span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">4</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">25</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">日，李衍黔任党总支书记、副总编辑，主持全面工作。夏立纯任党总支副书记、副社长，杜康宁任副总编辑、副社长，王冬生任副总编辑，王明光任党总支副书记，李文锦任副总编辑，张启航任副总编辑，杨书华、苏存计任编委成员。原总编辑、社长张秉谦为正处级调研员。</span></div>
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">10</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，举办山西教育报刊社成立四十周年庆典活动，省委书记胡富国、省长孙文盛、国家教委副主任柳斌、副省长王昕、省人大常委宋玉岫、省教委主任曹福成等题词；著名书画家赵延绪、杨秀珍、林鹏、卫俊秀、赵梅生、徐文达、王朝瑞、赵望进、田树苌等题词。</span></div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 49.9pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" width="67">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1997</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">年</span></div>
            </td>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 371.4pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" valign="top" width="495">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">12</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，《小学语文教学》首次被省委宣传部、省新闻出版局评为</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">“</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">山西省一级期刊</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">”</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">。</span></div>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 49.9pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" width="67">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">1999</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">年</span></div>
            </td>
            <td style="border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 2.25pt; background-color: transparent; padding-left: 2.25pt; width: 371.4pt; padding-right: 2.25pt; border-top: windowtext 1pt solid; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 2.25pt" valign="top" width="495">
            <div style="line-height: 115%; layout-grid-mode: both" align="left"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">10</span><span style="line-height: 115%; color: black; font-size: 9pt">月，《小学语文教学》被国家新闻出版总署评为第二届百种重点社科期刊。</span></div>
